title: Glycerine
meta_description:
Glycerine is a viscose, clear, colourless liquid with a slightly sweet taste._x000D_
_x000D_
It is mainly used to soften icing but can also be added to cake recipes where flour is used to create a softer crumb texture. Glycerine also helps to prevent sugar crystalliz
meta_keywords: glycerine, soften, icing, royal icing,ingredients, cake, baking supplies, basic, baking ingredients, baking, essential baking, gluten free, home baking
description:
Dr. Oetker Glycerine is mainly used to prevent a very hard set with royal icing but can also be added to cake recipes to keep your baking moist for longer. Glycerine also helps to prevent sugar crystallization in candy making._x000D_
To prevent royal icing from setting too firm on your home bakes add 1 teaspoon of Glycerine per 500g (1 lb) icing after the icing forms stiff peaks.

When adding to cakes, use 1 teaspoon of glycerine per 100g flour.

Available in a 38ml bottle.

Allergy Advice
No allergens for this product.

Due to possible ingredient updates, please always check allergen information on the packaging.

Dr. Oetker Free Range Egg White Powder is a versatile ingredient for use in all your recipes in place of fresh egg whites. It is ideal for meringues, royal icing and other sweet and savoury recipes - no more wasted left over yolks! 

Dr. Oetker Free Range Egg White Powder is packed in convenient individual sachets to keep the product fresh for each use. Each multipack contains 4 individual sachets. Each 5g sachet is the equivalent to 1 egg white. Each sachet multipack comes with a free recipe card, with a delicious and creative recipe idea. 

Egg White Powder is made from pasteurised egg whites. It can be used as a convenient alternative to fresh egg whites and has the added benefit of pasteurisation.

description:
Dr. Oetker Ground Arrowroot is ideal as a general thickener for sweet and savoury recipes. Ground Arrowroot is an essential ingredient for thickening glazes, as it remains clear and transparent, unlike cornflour which can give a cloudy result. 

Perfect for convenience and freshness, Dr. Oetker Ground Arrowroot Sachet Multipack includes 6 individual sachets of Ground Arrowroot. Each 8g sachet contains one convenient measured level tablespoon. Each sachet multipack comes with a free recipe card, with a delicious and creative recipe idea.

title: Gelatine Sachet Multipack
meta_description: Gelatine is a versatile setting agent used in a wide variety of sweet and savoury baking recipes. It is ideal for soufflés, jellies, homemade ice cream, mousses, cheesecakes, terrines, flans and pies. The powdered Gelatine is packed in 12g individual sach
meta_keywords: gelatine, beef, sachet, setting, agent, jelly, mousse, flan, pie, ingredients, baking supplies, basic, baking ingredients, baking, essential baking, gluten free, home baking
description:
Dr. Oetker Gelatine is a versatile setting agent used in a wide variety of sweet and savoury recipes. It is ideal for soufflés, jellies, homemade ice cream, mousses, cheesecakes, terrines, flans and pies.

The powdered Gelatine is packed in 12g individual sachets to keep the product fresh for each use. Each multipack contains 3 sachets - each sachet is sufficient to set one pint (570ml) of liquid. 1 sachet is the equivalent of approximately 4 leaves of Gelatine. Each sachet multipack comes with a free recipe card, with a delicious and creative recipe idea.

Our collection of gelatines are used to form a smooth, gelled but elastic texture which is not sticky or brittle. Our range contains beef, pork and vegetarian gelatine which are suitable for a variety of diets and food preferences. In addition to powdered gelatine, our range also includes Platinum Grade Leaf Gelatine and Vege-Gel.

Allergy Advice
Contains Sulphur Dioxide. May also contain EGG and MILK.

Due to possible ingredient updates, please always check allergen information on the packaging.

Other Advice
Contains beef.
hint_no1: Use quantities of gelatine and liquid as stated in your recipe._x000D_
hint_no2: One sachet sets 1 pint (570ml) of liquid. To dissolve the gelatine, pour 115ml/8tbsp of hot water into a jug or small bowl. Sprinkle the gelatine onto the hot water. Always add gelatine to liquid, not the other way around. Stir briskly until thoroughly mixed. If gelatine does not thoroughly dissolve stand the jug or bowl in a pan of warm water over a low heat.
hint_no3: Never allow gelatine mixture to boil.
add_storage: Store in a cool, dry place.

meta_description:
_x000D_
Our superior pods are carefully picked by hand when they are at their most succulent and moist to ensure they retain and deliver the finest aromatic vanilla taste to baking and desserts. The richest flavour is derived from the longest pods and each pod
meta_keywords: vanilla, pods, select, flavours, cake, flavouring, unusual cake flavours, cupcake flavours, extracts,
description:
Dr. Oetker Select Vanilla Pods are carefully selected from the finest succulent pods of the Indian Ocean Island region.  Vanilla pods are the fruit of the orchid, used for centuries in many culinary applications. Our superior pods are carefully picked by hand when they are at their most succulent and moist to ensure they retain and deliver the finest aromatic vanilla taste to baking and desserts. The richest flavour is derived from the longest pods and each pod is selected for its size and natural oil content.

Dr. Oetker Select Vanilla Pods are perfect for use in recipes where an 'infusion' is required and can be used to flavour sugar, syrups, creams, sauces, custards and ice-creams. The finished dish will be enhanced with tiny black vanilla seeds from the pod._x000D_
The delightful flavour of vanilla is at the heart of a wide variety of baking and sweet cooking and is even becoming popular as an addition to savoury cooking.  It is a delicate and very important ingredient.

Each pack contains 2 vanilla pods.

Allergy Advice_x000D_ No allergens for this product.

shortdescription: The thin and crispy base, the rich toppings and the carefully selected ingredients gives Ristorante Pizza Quattro Formaggi the perfect pizzeria taste.

hint_no1:
Hints & Tips:_x000D_
Rotate the pizza 180 degrees halfway through cooking for an even cheese browning.
hint_no2:
Hints & Tips:_x000D_
If cooking more than 1 pizza, we suggest you use the fan setting on your oven.  If you do not have a fan oven, then we recommend that you cook each pizza on a separate shelf and swap the pizzas over in the oven halfway through cooking so that both pizzas will be ready to enjoy at the same time.
hint_no3:
Hints & Tips:_x000D_

meta_description: Vege-Gel is a vegetarian setting agent for use in a wide variety of sweet and savoury recipes including soufflés, jellies, mousses, cheesecakes, terrines, flans and pies.
meta_keywords: vegetarian, gelatine, gel, jelly, agent, setting, mousse, vege, meat free,ingredients, baking supplies, basic, baking ingredients, baking, essential baking, gluten free, home baking
description:
Dr. Oetker Vege-Gel is a vegetarian setting agent, ideal for use in a wide variety of sweet and savoury recipes including soufflés, jellies, mousses, cheesecakes, terrines, flans and pies. 

Dr. Oetker Vege-Gel is packed in individual sachets to keep the product fresh for each use. Each pack contains 3 sachets - each sachet is sufficient to set one pint (570 ml) of liquid. Each sachet multipack comes with a free recipe card, with a delicious and creative recipe idea.

Vege-Gel is a vegetarian alternative to gelatine and not a substitute. Therefore, it has to be used in a slightly different way to gelatine and it may be necessary to adapt your recipe, when using acidic liquids or vinegar, use two sachets for best results. When dissolving in fruit juice, heat to near boiling point and cool quickly to aid setting.

Our collection of gelatines are used to form a smooth, gelled but elastic texture which is not sticky or brittle. Our range contains beef, pork and vegetarian gelatine which are suitable for a variety of diets and food preferences. 

Allergy Advice_x000D_ May contain Egg and Milk

Due to possible ingredient updates, please always check allergen information on the packaging.

Dr. Oetker Bicarbonate of Soda is a gentle raising agent for use in gingerbread, parkin, cookies, soda bread and a wide range of other recipes. It can be used to make a simple baking powder by using one part Bicarbonate of Soda to 2 parts Cream of Tartar.

'Bicarb' is a store cupboard essential which has also traditionally been popular for its usefulness around the house as well as for baking.  It is a great 'natural' cleaner, deodouriser and mild abrasive. Use in solution to clean fridges, microwaves, teapots, cafetieres, glassware and kitchen utensils.

Available in a resealable container of 200g as well as sachet multipack.

shortdescription: The thin and crispy base, the rich toppings and the carefully selected ingredients give Ristorante Pizza Mozzarella the perfect pizzeria taste
description: Experience the taste of an Italian Pizzeria with our thin and crispy, Italian style pizza, deliciously topped with mozzarella and Edam cheeses, cherry tomatoes and basil...
hint_no1:
Hints & Tips:_x000D_
Rotate the pizza 180 degrees halfway through cooking for an even cheese browning.
hint_no2:
Hints & Tips:_x000D_
If cooking more than 1 pizza, we suggest you use the fan setting on your oven. If you do not have a fan oven, then we recommend that you cook each pizza on a separate shelf and swap the pizzas over in the oven half way through cooking so that both pizzas will be ready to enjoy at the same time.
hint_no3:
Hints & Tips:_x000D_
Straight from the oven allow the pizza to cool on a cooling rack for 1 minute before serving.  This allows any steam to escape from the base and prevent it from softening.

title: Easy Swirl Vanilla Cupcake Icing
meta_description: Dr. Oetker Easy Swirl Vanilla Cupcake Icing is a light vanilla flavoured buttercream style icing that is ready to use straight from the can.
meta_keywords: Easy Swirl, vanilla, cupcake icing, ready to use, buttercream style, buttercream,  cake icing ideas, cupcake icing, biscuit icing, vanilla icing, fairy cake icing, cupcake icing, cup cake icing, easy icing, easy cake icing, simple cake icing
description:
Dr. Oetker Easy Swirl Vanilla Cupcake Icing is a light vanilla flavour buttercream style icing that is ready to use straight from the can.

The incredibly easy aerosol format allows you to create beautiful piped cupcakes and decorate biscuits, brownies and cookies, without the fuss and mess of using an icing bag and nozzle.

Easy Swirl Cupcake Icing comes with 4 nozzles that can be attached to create four fun piping effects including stars, swirls and lines.The nozzles also allow easy control and direction so anyone can create the perfect cupcake swirl.

Each can decorates 8 cupcakes or equivalent. Also available in Chocolate flavour and Pink.

Allergy Advice
No allergens for this product.

Due to possible ingredient updates, please always check allergen information on the packaging.

Other Advice
Suitable for Vegetarians.
_x000D_ _x000D_ _x000D_ _x000D_
hint_no1: To begin icing, hold the can horizontally, with the nozzle pointing down slightly. To pipe, press down firmly on the tip of the nozzle using your index finger.
hint_no2: As a guide we recommend that one can will cover approximately 8 cupcakes depending on the size of the cupcakes and the desired effect you want to achieve.
hint_no3: WARNING: Pressurised container: Do not pierce or burn, even after use. Protect from sunlight. Do not expose to temperatures exceeding 50°C/122°F.
add_storage: Store in a cool, dry place.

description:
Dr. Oetker Cream of Tartar is an essential ingredient which helps to increase the volume and stability of whisked egg whites in meringue and soufflé recipes. It can also be used to make a simple baking powder by using 1 part Bicarbonate of Soda to 2 parts Cream of Tartar.

Perfect for convenience and freshness, Dr. Oetker Cream of Tartar Sachet Multipack includes 6 individual sachets of Cream of Tartar. Each 5g sachet contains one convenient measured level teaspoon. Each sachet multipack comes with a free recipe card, with a delicious and creative recipe idea.
